    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>硬核派格斗体验</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《终极复仇》以现代技术和设计重现了经典硬核系格斗玩法。以90年代的传奇街机佳作为灵感来源，将动作游戏的连击技巧、精准出招和凌厉节奏推向极致。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891090/extras/4d4a6f3f617cfad7f9c92706ca9d7003.poster.avif?t=1761755487\" width=612 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891090/extras/4d4a6f3f617cfad7f9c92706ca9d7003.webm?t=1761755487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891090/extras/4d4a6f3f617cfad7f9c92706ca9d7003.mp4?t=1761755487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >伦敦已经沦为臭名昭著的Syndic8的地盘。身怀绝技的克莱尔·斯帕克斯原本过着平静的校园生活，然而妹妹被绑架使她被迫卷入了混乱的街头争斗。她与前职业摔跤手米勒·T·威廉姆斯和街头拳手杜克·桑丘联合，在危机四伏的伦敦街巷杀出一条血路，誓让一切挡路敌人付出代价！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891090/extras/82c855511fb96b80bd49bd4894723ad6.poster.avif?t=1761755487\" width=612 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891090/extras/82c855511fb96b80bd49bd4894723ad6.webm?t=1761755487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891090/extras/82c855511fb96b80bd49bd4894723ad6.mp4?t=1761755487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>选择你的打手</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >克莱尔·斯帕克斯：迅捷灵巧，擅长拳脚功夫，武艺高强</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >杜克·桑丘：老道的格斗家，出拳凶猛利落，身材魁梧</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >米勒·T·威廉姆斯：前职业摔跤手，享受纯粹的暴力与破坏</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每位角色都有独特连招与打击感。掌握格挡、连击、冲刺攻击等格斗技巧，在多种游戏模式中不断磨炼自己吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891090/extras/81fe46bd4acec926b28ad328b2da5ce2.poster.avif?t=1761755487\" width=612 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891090/extras/81fe46bd4acec926b28ad328b2da5ce2.webm?t=1761755487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891090/extras/81fe46bd4acec926b28ad328b2da5ce2.mp4?t=1761755487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>热血街头格斗之旅</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《终极复仇》完美还原了街机格斗游戏中的震撼视觉特效、热血配乐与畅快打击感。在精致华丽的复古像素艺术中，感受精准流畅的绝妙操作体验。让Utah Saints、Featurecast和Krafty Kuts共同打造的摇滚劲曲点燃你的战斗激情！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论单打独斗还是并肩作战，这都是一场纯粹畅快的街机格斗之旅。强者只用拳头说话。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891090/extras/62a8be4a2bf1152eb487323b8c9e98a3.poster.avif?t=1761755487\" width=612 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891090/extras/62a8be4a2bf1152eb487323b8c9e98a3.webm?t=1761755487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891090/extras/62a8be4a2bf1152eb487323b8c9e98a3.mp4?t=1761755487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快节奏经典硬核格斗玩法</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >三位可选角色，多种组合技</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持本地合作游玩</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >四种可选游玩模式：街机、生存、对战、Boss Rush</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >六个敌人密布的战斗街区</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >三种难度设定与丰富可解锁内容</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >英国本地乐队演绎独家震撼原声带</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
